<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="favicon.svg">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <meta property="og:title" content="The Hale Dynasty — Archive">
  <meta property="og:description" content="A fictional private archive of the Hale family of Worcestershire, England. Nine centuries. Ten volumes. One family. — MSS. Hale-Marsh Collection, Bodleian Libraries.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://the-hale-dynasty.vercel.app/crests/main_family_crest.png">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://the-hale-dynasty.vercel.app">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="The Hale Dynasty — Archive">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="A fictional private archive of the Hale family of Worcestershire, England. Nine centuries. Ten volumes. One family.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://the-hale-dynasty.vercel.app/crests/main_family_crest.png">
  <title>The Hale Dynasty — Archive</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>html { font-size: 18px; }

    
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --gold: #C8A83C;
      --gold-dim: #9A7A28;
      --gold-bright: #E8C84C;
      --bg: #0E0C0A;
      --bg-mid: #1A1612;
      --bg-box: #1E1A14;
      --text-dim: #6A5A48;
      --text-mid: #8A7A62;
      --text-light: #B8A888;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: pageIn 1.4s ease 0.4s forwards;
    
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    @keyframes pageIn { to { opacity: 1; } }

    /* ── ACCESS HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .access-header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1E1A12;
      padding: 9px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .access-status { color: #3A7A3A; }
    .access-clock { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

    /* ── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .hero {
      padding: 60px 40px 30px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 16% 18%, rgba(141, 53, 38, 0.16), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 14%, rgba(101, 118, 134, 0.12), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(228, 212, 182, 0.05), transparent 38%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      max-width: 1240px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(420px, 560px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: stretch;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-ledger {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 28px 18px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(231, 219, 194, 0.98), rgba(212, 194, 163, 0.98)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0, transparent 34px, rgba(107, 80, 44, 0.08) 34px, rgba(107, 80, 44, 0.08) 35px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.34);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 52px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
    }

    .hero-ledger-top {
      position: relative;
      padding-top: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero-ledger-top::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(95, 36, 26, 0.26), transparent);
    }

    .hero-ledger-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding-left: 10px;
    }

    .hero-ledger-ref {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
    }

    .hero-ledger::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.15);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-ledger::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 22px;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(143, 53, 38, 0.38), transparent);
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-ledger-body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(180px, 235px) minmax(240px, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-ledger-copy {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 0;
      padding-right: 4px;
    }

    .hero-thesis {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 18px 0 18px 10px;
      text-align: left;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-thesis::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 28px;
      bottom: 28px;
      left: -12px;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(164, 89, 70, 0.2), transparent);
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.64em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(116, 68, 42, 0.72);
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .hero-ledger-sub {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58em;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(87, 74, 58, 0.68);
    }

    .hero-stamp {
      width: 78px;
      height: 78px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(95, 36, 26, 0.3);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 32% 28%, rgba(255,255,255,0.32), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle, rgba(138, 41, 30, 0.18), rgba(109, 33, 24, 0.04) 62%, transparent 64%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transform: rotate(-8deg);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 18px rgba(95,36,26,0.12);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .hero-stamp-inner {
      width: 62px;
      height: 62px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(95,36,26,0.36);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.74em;
      color: rgba(95,36,26,0.72);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }

    .hero-crest-frame {
      position: relative;
      padding: 12px 12px 10px;
      margin: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(95, 36, 26, 0.16);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.36), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), rgba(174, 151, 117, 0.06));
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-crest-frame::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(95, 36, 26, 0.1);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-crest-frame::after {
      content: 'Recovered crest impression';
      position: absolute;
      right: 10px;
      bottom: 8px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.46em;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(87, 74, 58, 0.56);
    }

    .ornament {
      color: rgba(143, 53, 38, 0.74);
      font-size: 0.84em;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .main-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.82em, 3.15vw, 2.8em);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #5f241a;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.86em;
      color: rgba(95, 66, 40, 0.82);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .hero-divider {
      width: 56px; height: 1px;
      background: rgba(143, 53, 38, 0.38);
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .dates-line {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.04em;
      color: #3f4c5d;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.56em;
      color: rgba(79, 66, 52, 0.76);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .hero-note {
      max-width: 38rem;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 1.08em;
      line-height: 1.82;
      color: rgba(223, 212, 188, 0.92);
      font-style: normal;
    }

    .hero-thesis-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.45em, 2.8vw, 2.25em);
      color: #d4c39a;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      max-width: 13ch;
    }

    .hero-thesis-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-thesis-list li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(208, 193, 159, 0.8);
      font-size: 0.9em;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .hero-thesis-list li::before {
      content: '•';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      color: rgba(164, 89, 70, 0.9);
    }

    .hero-context {
      max-width: 34rem;
      border-left: 2px solid rgba(164, 89, 70, 0.42);
      padding-left: 16px;
      color: rgba(208, 193, 159, 0.62);
      font-size: 0.86em;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .hero-context-note {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(208, 193, 159, 0.44);
    }

    .matilda-quote {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #e0c48c;
      font-size: 1.08em;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .matilda-attr {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7em;
      color: rgba(197, 178, 141, 0.62);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .section-intro {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      padding: 0 30px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.76);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.05em, 2.2vw, 1.45em);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: #dbc796;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .section-copy {
      max-width: 60ch;
      font-size: 0.84em;
      line-height: 1.72;
      color: rgba(216, 202, 172, 0.68);
    }

    /* ── ARCHIVE SEARCH ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .search-section {
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    .search-panel {
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.22);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(33,29,25,0.96), rgba(18,16,13,0.98)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 18%);
      padding: 22px 22px 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }
    .search-panel::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 20%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0, transparent 29px, rgba(111,76,39,0.05) 29px, rgba(111,76,39,0.05) 30px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .search-heading {
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.74);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .search-heading::before, .search-heading::after { content: none; }

    .search-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.02em, 2vw, 1.34em);
      color: #dcc58f;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .search-copy {
      max-width: 58ch;
      font-size: 0.82em;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(212,198,165,0.67);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .search-bar-wrap {
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.22);
      background: rgba(15, 12, 10, 0.82);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .search-bar-wrap:focus-within {
      border-color: rgba(208, 170, 122, 0.48);
    }

    .search-icon {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 1em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      padding: 0 14px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    #archiveSearch {
      flex: 1;
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      padding: 13px 4px 13px 0;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.86em;
      color: #D4C8A0;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    #archiveSearch::placeholder { color: #3C3020; }

    .search-shortcut {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      color: rgba(170, 140, 102, 0.46);
      border: 1px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.18);
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-right: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .search-hint {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      color: rgba(170, 140, 102, 0.42);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .search-hint span { color: rgba(218, 190, 136, 0.62); }

    /* ── SEARCH RESULTS ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .search-results {
      margin-top: 14px;
      display: none;
    }

    .result-count {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.74em;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-left: 4px;
    }

    .result-card {
      display: block;
      background: #181410;
      border: 1px solid #252018;
      border-left: 3px solid #3A3020;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-left-color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
    }
    .result-card:hover {
      background: #201C14;
      border-left-color: #7A6020;
    }
    .result-card--special {
      border-left: 3px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.5);
      background: #14100A;
    }
    .result-card--special:hover {
      background: #1C1608;
      border-left-color: var(--gold);
    }

    .result-ref {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.74em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .result-title {
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #C0B080;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .result-card--special .result-title { color: var(--gold); }
    .result-date {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.76em;
      color: #4A4028;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }
    .result-card--special .result-date { color: #7A6A28; }
    .result-excerpt {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #5A5038;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }
    .result-card--special .result-excerpt { color: #7A6A40; }
    .result-alert {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.76em;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.2);
      animation: alertPulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes alertPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; }
      50% { opacity: 1; }
    }
    .result-open {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.74em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .result-card:hover .result-open { color: var(--gold-dim); }

    .no-results {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      padding: 14px 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    /* ── ARCHIVE INSTRUCTION ───────────────────────────────── */
    .archive-instruction {
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 30px 22px;
    }
    .archive-instruction::before, .archive-instruction::after {
      content: none;
    }

    /* ── ARCHIVE GRID ──────────────────────────────────────── */
    .archive-grid {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 30px 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .archive-clusters {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 30px 60px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 28px;
    }
    .archive-cluster {
      position: relative;
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.22);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(26,23,19,0.98), rgba(16,14,11,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 14%, rgba(164,89,70,0.06), transparent 16%);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }
    .archive-cluster::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.05);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .archive-cluster::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 22px;
      right: 22px;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.88), rgba(215,186,134,0.22), transparent 78%);
    }
    .archive-cluster--continue::after {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(116,145,165,0.7), rgba(215,186,134,0.18), transparent 78%);
    }
    .archive-cluster--later::after {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(90,122,70,0.7), rgba(215,186,134,0.18), transparent 78%);
    }
    .archive-cluster-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(150px, 210px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.08);
    }
    .archive-cluster-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.72);
    }
    .archive-cluster-copy {
      max-width: 54ch;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      line-height: 1.72;
      color: rgba(222,210,181,0.68);
    }
    .archive-cluster-copy strong {
      color: rgba(221,197,144,0.82);
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .archive-cluster-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .archive-box-note {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.54em;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.68);
    }
    .archive-box--continue .archive-box-note {
      color: rgba(116,145,165,0.72);
    }

    /* ── ARCHIVE BOX ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    @keyframes boxReveal {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }

    .archive-box {
      position: relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(27,23,18,0.98), rgba(16,14,11,0.98)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(164,89,70,0.06), transparent 18%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.22);
      overflow: hidden;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
      /* Start hidden, reveal in sequence */
      opacity: 0;
      animation: boxReveal 0.5s ease forwards;
    }
    .archive-box-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.5em;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(242, 231, 204, 0.86);
      background: rgba(104, 39, 28, 0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(206, 173, 127, 0.34);
      padding: 4px 7px;
      z-index: 3;
    }
    .archive-box--continue .archive-box-badge {
      background: rgba(55, 74, 96, 0.84);
    }
    .archive-box--later .archive-box-badge {
      background: rgba(60, 79, 48, 0.82);
    }
    .archive-box--feature {
      border-color: rgba(206, 173, 127, 0.26);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .archive-box--feature .box-label {
      padding-top: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .archive-box:nth-child(1)  { animation-delay: 1.0s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(2)  { animation-delay: 1.12s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(3)  { animation-delay: 1.24s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(4)  { animation-delay: 1.36s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(5)  { animation-delay: 1.48s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(6)  { animation-delay: 1.60s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(7)  { animation-delay: 1.72s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(8)  { animation-delay: 1.84s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(9)  { animation-delay: 1.96s; }
    .archive-box:nth-child(10) { animation-delay: 2.08s; }

    .archive-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.24);
      border-color: rgba(189, 153, 108, 0.34);
    }
    .archive-box:hover .box-title { color: var(--gold-bright); }
    .archive-box:hover .box-spine-inner { opacity: 1; }

    /* ── BANNER IMAGE PREVIEW ─────────────────────────────── */
    .box-banner {
      width: 100%;
      height: 72px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .box-banner img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: sepia(0.55) contrast(1.1) brightness(0.55);
      transition: filter 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
      display: block;
    }
    .archive-box:hover .box-banner img {
      filter: sepia(0.3) contrast(1.15) brightness(0.78);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    .box-banner-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg,
        rgba(10,8,4,0.05) 0%,
        rgba(10,8,4,0.7) 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    /* Vol label overlaid on banner bottom */
    .box-banner-vol {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 7px;
      left: 14px;
      right: 10px;
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 0.52em;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(180,150,60,0.75);
      pointer-events: none;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
    }

    /* Vol. X — the discovery box */
    .archive-box--discovery {
      border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.2);
    }
    .archive-box--discovery:hover {
      border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.5);
    }

    .discovery-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px; right: 8px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.5em;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.4);
      padding: 2px 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .box-spine {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 5px;
    }
    .box-label { padding: 16px 18px 18px 24px; }
    .box-label {
      position: relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(247,239,221,0.035), transparent 18%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0, transparent 24px, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 24px, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 25px);
    }
    .box-vol {
      display: none; /* vol is now shown in banner overlay */
    }
    .box-title {
      font-size: 0.94em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #d8c490;
      line-height: 1.34;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .box-dates {
      display: none; /* dates shown in banner vol overlay */
    }
    .box-divider {
      width: 28px; height: 1px;
      background: #302818;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .box-desc {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.76em;
      color: rgba(220,206,177,0.62);
      line-height: 1.62;
    }
    .box-enter {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .archive-box:hover .box-enter { color: var(--gold-dim); }

    /* ── CINEMATIC INTRO SPLASH ─────────────────────────────── */
    .splash {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(186,145,44,0.18), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 58%, rgba(111,47,36,0.16), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050403 0%, #090705 45%, #120c08 100%);
      z-index: 900;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: all;
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease;
    }
    .splash.out { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .splash-backdrop {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .splash-backdrop::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 3.5vh 3.5vw;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,192,136,0.07);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(216,192,136,0.03),
        inset 0 0 120px rgba(216,192,136,0.02);
    }
    .splash-backdrop::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 7vh;
      width: min(86vw, 1120px);
      height: min(92vh, 980px);
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 18%, rgba(216,192,136,0.24) 0%, rgba(216,192,136,0.08) 18%, transparent 56%);
      clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 74% 14%, 84% 34%, 84% 100%, 16% 100%, 16% 34%, 26% 14%);
      filter: blur(16px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease 0.1s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-backdrop::after { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-cathedral {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 6vh 10vw 12vh;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease 0.2s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-cathedral { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-cathedral::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,192,136,0.12);
      clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 72% 14%, 82% 33%, 82% 100%, 18% 100%, 18% 33%, 28% 14%);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(216,192,136,0.03),
        0 0 40px rgba(216,192,136,0.04);
    }
    .splash-cathedral::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 42px 52px 36px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,192,136,0.09);
      clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 70% 15%, 78% 34%, 78% 100%, 22% 100%, 22% 34%, 30% 15%);
    }
    .splash-pillars {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .splash-pillars::before,
    .splash-pillars::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 11vh;
      bottom: 10vh;
      width: 14vw;
      max-width: 180px;
      min-width: 82px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(216,192,136,0.05), rgba(216,192,136,0.015)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          to right,
          transparent 0 18px,
          rgba(216,192,136,0.08) 18px 19px,
          transparent 19px 37px
        );
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease 0.4s;
    }
    .splash-pillars::before { left: 5vw; }
    .splash-pillars::after { right: 5vw; }
    .splash.go .splash-pillars::before,
    .splash.go .splash-pillars::after { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-rings,
    .splash-rings::before,
    .splash-rings::after {
      position: absolute;
      content: '';
      left: 50%;
      top: 9vh;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .splash-rings {
      width: min(44vw, 520px);
      height: min(64vh, 700px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,192,136,0.12);
      border-radius: 46% 46% 12px 12px / 18% 18% 12px 12px;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.4s ease 0.3s;
    }
    .splash-rings::before {
      inset: 26px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216,192,136,0.1);
      border-radius: 46% 46% 12px 12px / 18% 18% 12px 12px;
    }
    .splash-rings::after {
      inset: 78px;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(111,47,36,0.22);
      border-radius: 46% 46% 12px 12px / 18% 18% 12px 12px;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-rings { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-axis {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 50%;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(216,192,136,0.24), rgba(216,192,136,0.08), transparent);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 0.6s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-axis { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-stage {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10vh 24px 16vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .splash-crest {
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.4s ease, transform 1.4s ease;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      transform: translateY(22px) scale(0.9);
      width: 118px;
      height: 132px;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-crest { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-overline {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.66em;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(216,192,136,0.58);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 0.35s, transform 1.2s ease 0.35s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-overline { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-era {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      letter-spacing: 0.54em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(205,181,132,0.76);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 0.65s, transform 1.2s ease 0.65s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-era { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.8em, 11vw, 9.4em);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: #E9CA6C;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-shadow:
        0 0 46px rgba(216,192,136,0.12),
        0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
        0 0 2px rgba(255,230,166,0.3);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.98);
      transition: opacity 1.3s ease 0.85s, transform 1.3s ease 0.85s;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-title { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-deck {
      margin: 22px auto 0;
      max-width: 18ch;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.65em, 3.2vw, 2.7em);
      line-height: 1.12;
      color: rgba(244,232,205,0.94);
      text-wrap: balance;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 1.25s, transform 1.2s ease 1.25s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-deck { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-line {
      width: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(235,205,126,0.96), transparent);
      margin: 36px auto 30px;
      opacity: 0.94;
      transition: width 1.4s ease 1.75s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-line { width: min(480px, 66vw); }
    .splash-thesis {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      letter-spacing: 0.42em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(224,198,146,0.72);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(14px);
      transition: opacity 1s ease 2s, transform 1s ease 2s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-thesis { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .splash-begin {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72em;
      color: rgba(176,84,55,0.98);
      letter-spacing: 0.46em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease 2.45s;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-begin { opacity: 1; }
    /* Mobile splash adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .splash-stage { padding: 12vh 18px 17vh; }
      .splash-cathedral { inset: 10vh 7vw 16vh; }
      .splash-pillars::before,
      .splash-pillars::after { width: 18vw; min-width: 46px; top: 14vh; bottom: 13vh; }
      .splash-overline { font-size: 0.54em; letter-spacing: 0.22em; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 28ch; }
      .splash-crest { width: 84px; height: 94px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .splash-era { font-size: 0.62em; letter-spacing: 0.28em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
      .splash-title { font-size: clamp(2.8em, 14vw, 5em); letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
      .splash-deck { font-size: 1.18em; max-width: 17ch; margin-top: 18px; }
      .splash-line { margin: 24px auto 18px; }
      .splash-thesis { font-size: 0.62em; letter-spacing: 0.24em; }
      .splash-begin { font-size: 0.62em; letter-spacing: 0.24em; }
    }
    .splash-sound-btn {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: max(28px, calc(28px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom)));
      right: 28px;
      background: rgba(15,10,7,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.28);
      border-radius: 50%; width: 52px; height: 52px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer; color: rgba(200,168,60,0.55);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, opacity 0.8s ease 3s;
      opacity: 0; padding: 0;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      touch-action: manipulation;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-sound-btn { opacity: 1; }
    .splash-sound-btn:hover { border-color: #C8A83C; color: #C8A83C; }
    .splash-sound-btn.playing { border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.7); color: rgba(200,168,60,0.9); }
    .splash-sound-label {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: max(44px, calc(44px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom)));
      left: 30px;
      transform: none;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      color: rgba(200,168,60,0);
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: color 1s ease 0.6s;
      z-index: 900;
    }
    .splash.go .splash-sound-label { color: rgba(200,168,60,0.35); }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .splash-sound-btn { width: 48px; height: 48px; bottom: max(22px, calc(22px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom))); right: 18px; left: auto; transform: none; }
      .splash-sound-label { bottom: max(38px, calc(38px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom))); left: 18px; max-width: 50vw; line-height: 1.5; }
    }

    /* ── MATILDA EASTER EGG OVERLAY ────────────────────────── */
    .matilda-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
      z-index: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: background 1.6s ease, opacity 0.5s ease;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active {
      pointer-events: all;
      opacity: 1;
      background: rgba(2,1,0,0.96);
    }
    .matilda-overlay-glow {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 42%, rgba(200,168,60,0.09) 0%, transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 2.4s ease 1s;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .matilda-overlay-glow { opacity: 1; }

    /* Parchment fragment — only exists in this moment */
    .egg-parchment {
      max-width: 560px;
      width: 100%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 30%, #2A1E0A 0%, #1A1206 60%, #100E08 100%);
      border: 1px solid #3A2810;
      padding: 48px 52px 52px;
      position: relative;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(28px) scale(0.97);
      transition: opacity 1.6s ease 0.8s, transform 1.6s ease 0.8s;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-parchment { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .egg-parchment::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 6px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    /* Aged edge burn effect */
    .egg-parchment::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 0%, transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 100%, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 0%, transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 0%, transparent 25%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .egg-seal {
      width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 38% 35%, #B82020 0%, #7A0A0A 60%, #4A0606 100%);
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1s ease 1.8s;
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(120,10,10,0.3);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.72em;
      color: rgba(255,200,100,0.6);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-seal { opacity: 1; }

    .egg-line-1 {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(0.95em, 2.5vw, 1.35em);
      color: #C8A83C;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.75;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.4s ease 1.4s;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-line-1 { opacity: 1; }

    .egg-line-2 {
      font-size: clamp(0.82em, 2vw, 1em);
      color: #8A7A56;
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 2.8s;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-line-2 { opacity: 1; }

    .egg-line-3 {
      font-size: clamp(0.8em, 1.8vw, 0.92em);
      color: #5A4A30;
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease 4s;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-line-3 { opacity: 1; }

    .egg-attr {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6em;
      color: #3A2A10;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #2A1E08;
      padding-top: 18px;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1s ease 5.2s;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-attr { opacity: 1; }

    .egg-dismiss {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58em;
      color: #2A1E0A;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease 6.5s, color 0.2s;
      border: 1px solid #2A1E0A;
      padding: 8px 20px;
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-dismiss { opacity: 1; }
    .egg-dismiss:hover { color: #C8A83C; border-color: #4A3820; }

    @keyframes goldPulse {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(120,10,10,0.3); }
      50%       { box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(200,168,60,0.25), 0 0 60px rgba(200,168,60,0.1); }
    }
    .matilda-overlay.active .egg-seal {
      animation: goldPulse 4s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
    }

    /* ── PIG EASTER EGG OVERLAY ────────────────────────────── */
    .pig-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
      z-index: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: background 1.6s ease, opacity 0.5s ease;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    .pig-overlay.active {
      pointer-events: all;
      opacity: 1;
      background: rgba(2,2,0,0.96);
    }
    .pig-overlay .egg-parchment { background: rgba(30,20,5,0.7); border: 1px solid rgba(180,140,60,0.12); opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px) scale(0.97); transition: opacity 1.6s ease 0.8s, transform 1.6s ease 0.8s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-parchment { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-seal { color: rgba(200,168,60,0.45); font-size: 0.82em; letter-spacing: 0.28em; background: none; box-shadow: none; border-radius: 0; width: auto; height: auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.15); padding-bottom: 16px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.4s ease 0.4s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-seal { opacity: 1; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-line-1 { color: #B89A44; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.4s ease 1s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-line-1 { opacity: 1; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-line-2 { color: #7A6A3A; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.2s ease 2.4s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-line-2 { opacity: 1; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-line-3 { color: #5A4A28; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.2s ease 4s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-line-3 { opacity: 1; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-attr { color: #3A2E10; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1s ease 5.2s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-attr { opacity: 1; }
    .pig-overlay .egg-dismiss { color: #2A1E0A; border-color: #2A1E0A; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.8s ease 6.5s; }
    .pig-overlay.active .egg-dismiss { opacity: 1; }

    /* ── MYSTERY TRAIL ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .matilda-mystery {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    .mystery-inner {
      border: 1px dashed rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.26);
      padding: 20px 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(22,19,16,0.82), rgba(14,12,10,0.92));
    }
    .mystery-label {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.76em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .mystery-note {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #5A4A30;
    }

    .support-archive {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    .support-archive-shell {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(170, 119, 64, 0.34);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(46,32,22,0.98), rgba(20,15,11,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 18%, rgba(196,126,54,0.12), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 85%, rgba(111,47,36,0.12), transparent 22%);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 42px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
      padding: 28px 28px;
    }
    .support-archive-shell::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 11px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.05);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .support-archive-shell::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,126,54,0.96), rgba(230,198,126,0.44), transparent 84%);
    }
    .support-archive-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .support-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.66em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(218,164,89,0.9);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .support-title {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(2em, 3.5vw, 2.9em);
      line-height: 1.08;
      color: #F0DEB0;
    }
    .support-copy {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 58ch;
      font-size: 0.98em;
      line-height: 1.82;
      color: rgba(235,223,194,0.82);
    }
    .support-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .support-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-width: 246px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(230,188,84,0.56);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(113,63,25,0.98), rgba(66,35,18,0.98)),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,214,120,0.08), transparent);
      color: #F5E4B7;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.74em;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease, background 0.22s ease, color 0.22s ease;
      box-shadow:
        0 14px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.24),
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,226,154,0.08);
    }
    .support-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(243,205,108,0.8);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.28),
        0 0 22px rgba(200,168,60,0.14);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(137,77,28,0.98), rgba(78,42,20,0.98)),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,214,120,0.12), transparent);
      color: #FFF2D0;
    }
    .support-button-mark {
      font-size: 1.24em;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      color: #FFD36A;
    }
    .support-note {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.64em;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(218,188,136,0.68);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .archive-footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 34px 40px 56px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.16);
    }
    .footer-note {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75em;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      line-height: 2.2;
    }

    /* ── EXPLORE NAV (Map + Family Tree) ───────────────────── */
    .explore-nav {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      padding: 0 30px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .explore-shell {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
    }
    .explore-group {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 22px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.24);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(29,25,21,0.98), rgba(16,14,11,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 14%, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 16%);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .explore-group::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.06);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .explore-group::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.9), rgba(215,186,134,0.22), transparent 78%);
      opacity: 0.85;
    }
    .explore-group--world {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(25,24,22,0.98), rgba(15,14,12,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 14%, rgba(70,101,122,0.08), transparent 18%);
    }
    .explore-group--world::after {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(116,145,165,0.7), rgba(214,188,143,0.18), transparent 78%);
    }
    .explore-group--deep {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(28,24,20,0.98), rgba(15,13,11,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 14%, rgba(90,122,70,0.08), transparent 18%);
    }
    .explore-group-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(150px, 190px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      padding: 0 2px 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.08);
    }
    .explore-group-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.72);
    }
    .explore-group-copy {
      max-width: 56ch;
      font-size: 0.79em;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(222,210,181,0.68);
    }
    .explore-group-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .explore-group--primary .explore-group-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 0.9fr);
    }
    .explore-card {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(44,37,31,0.98), rgba(22,19,16,0.99)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 18%, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 18%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(138, 108, 70, 0.24);
      border-left: 3px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.5);
      padding: 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .explore-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214,188,143,0.06);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .explore-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(200,168,60,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .explore-card:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(56,45,36,0.99), rgba(25,21,17,0.99));
      border-color: rgba(206, 173, 127, 0.34);
      transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(2px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
    }
    .explore-card-icon {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      opacity: 0.72;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.16);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    }
    .explore-card:hover .explore-card-icon { opacity: 1; }
    .explore-card-text { flex: 1; }
    .explore-card-eyebrow {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.52em;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.64);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .explore-card-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.82em; color: #d7c38f;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .explore-card-sub {
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: rgba(224,211,182,0.72);
      line-height: 1.68;
      max-width: 40ch;
    }
    .explore-card-arrow {
      margin-left: auto; color: rgba(216,192,136,0.5);
      font-size: 1.2em; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      transition: color 0.2s, transform 0.15s; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .explore-card:hover .explore-card-arrow { color: var(--gold-dim); transform: translateX(4px); }
    .explore-card--primary {
      padding: 26px 24px;
      min-height: 188px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      border-left-width: 4px;
    }
    .explore-card--primary .explore-card-icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .explore-card--primary .explore-card-title {
      font-size: 1.08em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .explore-card--primary .explore-card-sub {
      font-size: 0.84em;
      max-width: 34ch;
    }
    .explore-card--utility {
      min-height: 114px;
    }
    .explore-group--world .explore-card {
      border-left-color: rgba(116,145,165,0.48);
    }
    .explore-group--deep .explore-card {
      border-left-color: rgba(90,122,70,0.48);
    }
    .explore-group--world .explore-card-icon {
      border-color: rgba(116,145,165,0.16);
    }
    .explore-group--deep .explore-card-icon {
      border-color: rgba(90,122,70,0.18);
    }

    /* ── START HERE ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .start-here-section {
      max-width: 940px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 30px 28px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .start-here-section::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: min(940px, calc(100% - 8px));
      height: 34px;
      margin: 0 auto 14px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.16), transparent 65%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0, transparent 22px, rgba(164,89,70,0.09) 22px, rgba(164,89,70,0.09) 23px);
      clip-path: polygon(2% 0, 98% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .start-here-box {
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.24);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(35,31,26,0.92), rgba(21,18,15,0.96)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 28%);
      padding: 24px 24px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .start-here-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 86% 20%, rgba(221,197,144,0.06), transparent 18%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .start-here-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.74);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .start-here-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.4vw, 1.5em);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: #dcc58f;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .start-here-copy {
      font-size: 0.89em;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(224,211,182,0.76);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      max-width: 62ch;
    }
    .start-here-main {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72em;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #f1e8d0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #7d3023, #612319);
      border: 1px solid #a35d4a;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .start-here-main:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8d3828, #6b261a);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(97,35,25,0.22);
    }
    .start-here-steps {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.14);
      padding-top: 12px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .start-here-steps a {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(164,89,70,0.16);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      min-height: 62px;
      transition: border-color 0.18s, background 0.18s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .start-here-steps a:hover {
      border-color: rgba(206,173,127,0.3);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .start-here-step-label {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.56em;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.64);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .start-here-step-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.78em;
      color: rgba(221,197,144,0.88);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    /* ── FEEDBACK PROMPT ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .feedback-prompt {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 6px 30px 34px;
    }
    .feedback-card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.22);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(31,28,24,0.96), rgba(18,16,13,0.98)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 16%, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 18%);
      padding: 20px 20px 18px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .feedback-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(164,89,70,0.08), transparent 18%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0, transparent 28px, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 28px, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 29px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .feedback-head {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.05em;
      color: #dcc58f;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .feedback-sub {
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: rgba(220,206,177,0.68);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .feedback-choice-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .feedback-choice-row input {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .feedback-choice {
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.2);
      color: rgba(200,168,60,0.55);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
      background: rgba(200,168,60,0.03);
    }
    .feedback-choice-row input:checked + .feedback-choice {
      border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.6);
      color: #E8C84C;
      background: rgba(200,168,60,0.1);
    }
    #feedbackConfusion {
      width: 100%;
      background: #110F0A;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.18);
      color: rgba(220,205,160,0.9);
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      line-height: 1.55;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      min-height: 92px;
      resize: vertical;
    }
    #feedbackConfusion::placeholder { color: rgba(200,168,60,0.24); }
    #feedbackConfusion:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.42);
    }
    .feedback-actions {
      margin-top: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .feedback-submit {
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.35);
      background: rgba(200,168,60,0.08);
      color: rgba(220,200,140,0.9);
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    }
    .feedback-submit:hover {
      border-color: rgba(200,168,60,0.6);
      color: #E8C84C;
      background: rgba(200,168,60,0.14);
    }
    .feedback-status {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58em;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(200,168,60,0.45);
    }

    /* ── THEMATIC READING PATHS ────────────────────────────── */
    .reading-paths-section {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 0; padding: 56px 30px 8px;
    }
    .reading-paths-heading {
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62em;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(164,89,70,0.76);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .reading-paths-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.02em, 2vw, 1.34em);
      color: #dcc58f;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .reading-paths-copy {
      max-width: 60ch;
      font-size: 0.84em;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: rgba(220,206,177,0.72);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .reading-paths-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .reading-paths-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .reading-path-card {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(31,28,24,0.96), rgba(18,16,13,0.98)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(164,89,70,0.06), transparent 20%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(111, 76, 39, 0.22);
      padding: 20px 18px 22px;
      position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .reading-path-card:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(36,31,27,0.98), rgba(20,17,14,0.98));
      border-color: rgba(189, 153, 108, 0.28);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }
    .reading-path-icon {
      font-size: 1.3em; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; opacity: 0.5;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    .reading-path-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.78em; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #C8A83C; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .reading-path-desc {
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.8em; line-height: 1.72;
      color: rgba(224,211,182,0.66); font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .reading-path-stops {
      list-style: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,168,60,0.06);
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
    .reading-path-stops li {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58em; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(216,192,136,0.34);
      padding: 3px 0;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .reading-path-stops li::before {
      content: '→'; color: rgba(200,168,60,0.15); flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .reading-path-stops a {
      color: rgba(200,168,60,0.35); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .reading-path-stops a:hover { color: #C8A83C; }

    /* ── ERA ART OVERLAY ON ARCHIVE BOXES ─────────────────── */
    .box-era-art {
      position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 12px;
      opacity: 0.07; pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .archive-box:hover .box-era-art { opacity: 0.16; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .access-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.56em; }
      .access-header span:nth-child(2),
      .access-header span:nth-child(3) { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 46px 20px 24px; }
      .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 18px; }
      .hero-ledger { padding: 22px 18px 18px; }
      .hero-ledger::after { display: none; }
      .hero-thesis::before { display: none; }
      .hero-ledger-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }
      .hero-ledger-meta { padding-left: 0; }
      .hero-stamp { width: 68px; height: 68px; }
      .hero-stamp-inner { width: 52px; height: 52px; font-size: 0.66em; }
      .hero-crest-frame { margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; padding: 16px 14px 18px; }
      .hero-thesis { padding: 0; }
      .hero-context { max-width: none; }
      .start-here-section::before { height: 22px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .start-here-section { padding: 0 16px 22px; }
      .start-here-box { padding: 16px 14px 14px; }
      .support-archive { padding: 0 16px; }
      .support-archive-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; align-items: start; }
      .support-actions { justify-content: flex-start; }
      .support-button { width: 100%; min-width: 0; }
      .support-note { text-align: left; }
      .start-here-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .feedback-prompt { padding: 6px 16px 24px; }
      .archive-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
      .archive-clusters { padding: 0 16px 48px; gap: 20px; }
      .archive-cluster { padding: 16px 14px 16px; }
      .archive-cluster-head { display: block; border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
      .archive-cluster-copy { margin-top: 6px; }
      .archive-cluster-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
      .main-title { font-size: 1.6em; }
      .mystery-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; text-align: center; }
      .search-section { padding: 0 16px; }
      .section-intro { padding: 0 16px; }
      .explore-nav { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 0 16px; }
      .explore-group { padding: 18px 16px 16px; }
      .explore-group-head { display: block; border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
      .explore-group-copy { margin-top: 6px; }
      .explore-group-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .dates-line { font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
      .hero-divider { margin: 0 0 14px; }
      .explore-card { padding: 14px 16px; gap: 12px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .explore-card-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
      .explore-card--primary { min-height: 0; padding: 18px 16px; }
      .explore-card--primary .explore-card-icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; }
      .explore-card-text { width: 100%; }
      .explore-card-title { font-size: 1.65em; line-height: 1.08; }
      .explore-card-sub { max-width: none; }
      .explore-card-arrow { align-self: flex-end; }
      .reading-paths-section { padding: 46px 16px 8px; }
      .archive-instruction { padding: 22px 16px 18px; }
    }
    /* ── SITE CREST LOGO ─────────────────────────────────── */
    .site-crest-hero {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 16px 22px rgba(95,36,26,0.12));
    }
    .crest-hero-img {
      width: clamp(220px, 24vw, 320px);
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      filter: sepia(0.22) saturate(0.92) contrast(1.02);
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 72% 80% at center, black 30%, transparent 100%);
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 72% 80% at center, black 30%, transparent 100%);
    }
    .header-crest {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .header-crest-svg {
      opacity: 0.6;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .header-crest-name {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.65em;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: rgba(200,168,60,0.45);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    </style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="features.css">
  <script defer src="/_vercel/insights/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-transition-overlay" id="pageOverlay"></div>

  <header class="access-header">
    <div class="header-crest"><svg class="header-crest-svg" width="16" height="18" viewBox="0 0 72 80"><path d="M36 4 L66 16 L66 46 Q66 66 36 76 Q6 66 6 46 L6 16 Z" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,168,60,0.7)" stroke-width="2"/><text x="36" y="48" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Cinzel,serif" font-size="22" fill="rgba(200,168,60,0.7)" font-weight="700">H</text></svg><span class="header-crest-name">Hale Dynasty</span></div>
    <span>Bodleian Library, Oxford &nbsp;·&nbsp; MSS. Hale-Marsh Collection</span>
    <span>Ref: Hale-Marsh 1–10 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Special Collections</span>
    <span class="access-status access-clock">● Access granted</span>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-ledger">
        <div class="hero-ledger-top">
          <div class="hero-ledger-meta">
            <div class="hero-ledger-ref">
              <div class="hero-kicker">MSS. Hale-Marsh 1-10 · Reading Room Copy</div>
              <div class="hero-ledger-sub">Accession noted March 2026 · Restricted copy released</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-stamp" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="hero-stamp-inner">H·M</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-ledger-body">
          <div class="hero-crest-frame">
            <div class="site-crest-hero">
              <img src="crests/main_family_crest.png" class="crest-hero-img" alt="Hale Family Coat of Arms — Per Saecula Manimus">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-ledger-copy">
            <span class="ornament">✦ &nbsp; ✦ &nbsp; ✦</span>
            <h1 class="main-title">THE HALE DYNASTY</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">An Archive of Inheritance in Ten Volumes</p>
            <div class="hero-divider"></div>
            <div class="dates-line">1066 &mdash; 2026</div>
            <p class="tagline">958 Years &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Ten Volumes &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; One Family</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-thesis">
        <p class="hero-note">For nine and a half centuries they kept the land, buried their dead, made their bargains, withheld their tenderness, and left a record longer than memory.</p>
        <h2 class="hero-thesis-title">An English family. A conquered estate. A record that refuses to stay closed.</h2>
        <ul class="hero-thesis-list">
          <li>Begin with a Norman chronicle, then watch inheritance harden into duty, secrecy, grief, and return.</li>
          <li>Each volume changes century, voice, and pressure, but the line holds long enough to be read.</li>
          <li>This archive is not a glossary to inspect from outside. It is an inheritance to enter.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="hero-context">
          <p class="matilda-quote">&ldquo;Keep asking. Keep the land. See to the pig.&rdquo;</p>
          <p class="matilda-attr">— Matilda of Halecroft, c. 1390</p>
          <div class="hero-context-note">Whole generations vanished. The instruction remained.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-here-section" aria-label="Start here">
    <div class="start-here-box">
      <div class="start-here-kicker">First Visit</div>
      <h2 class="start-here-title">Start Here: the opening path through the archive</h2>
      <p class="start-here-copy">Start with the founding chronicle, continue into the next century, then use the family tree once the line of descent is already familiar.</p>
      <a href="era-I.html" class="start-here-main" data-track="start_story_click" data-track-label="start_here_main">Start the story (3-5 min)</a>
      <ul class="start-here-steps">
        <li>
          <a href="era-I.html" data-track="guided_path_click" data-track-label="step_1_era_i">
            <span class="start-here-step-label">Step 1</span>
            <span class="start-here-step-title">Vol. I - The Chronicle</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="era-II.html" data-track="guided_path_click" data-track-label="step_2_era_ii">
            <span class="start-here-step-label">Step 2</span>
            <span class="start-here-step-title">Vol. II - The House of Hale</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="family-tree.html" data-track="guided_path_click" data-track-label="step_3_tree">
            <span class="start-here-step-label">Step 3</span>
            <span class="start-here-step-title">Family Tree - Follow the line</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       EXPLORE NAV — Family Tree + Map
       ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="explore-shell" aria-label="Explore the Dynasty">
    <div class="section-intro">
      <div class="section-kicker">Beyond The Volumes</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Read the family through places, faces, papers, and the apparatus built around them.</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">These are not side quests so much as alternative doors into the same record: the line of descent, the estate it circles, the portraits imagined from the archive, and the research notebooks left in its wake.</p>
    </div>
  <div class="explore-nav">
    <div class="explore-group explore-group--primary">
      <div class="explore-group-head">
