        <span style="font-family:'Courier New',monospace; font-size:0.62em; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(200,168,60,0.3);">Your Progress Through the Archive</span>
        <span id="progress-count" style="font-family:'Courier New',monospace; font-size:0.62em; letter-spacing:0.12em; color:rgba(200,168,60,0.4);">0 / 10 volumes</span>
